    p.subtitle You can install this plugin from the community plugins, manually,
     | or using the BRAT plugin. Please note that in order to use the plugin, you
     | need an account on relay.md and have to obtain your access key from the
     | profile page.

   .card.block
    .card-header
     .card-header-title Installing from community plugins
    .card-content
     p.block The
      span.tag.is-light relay.md
      | plugin is available directly from the community plugins repo. You can
      | either search for it in Obsidian, or simply click the button below to
      | have the plugin screen opened and relay.md pre-selected.
     p.has-text-centered.block
      a.button.is-info.is-medium.is-rounded(href="obsidian://show-plugin?id=relay-md") Relay.md Plugin in Obsidian

